Story Discovery Engine
What It Is
For each scholarship prompt, MyScholarHack identifies which real experiences best match what’s being asked.
Why It Matters
Students don’t struggle because they lack stories — they struggle because they don’t know which story to use.
This removes guesswork and builds confidence fast.
